is comment about sarah palin and her cancer on the republican party brooks yeah i do i think it was some lunch affair for some magazine and i was just mouthing off and so i  im not a fan of hers but thats a little strong   brooks david march   no uturns the new york times retrieved september     pareene alex blow up the times oped page and start again salon retrieved august     sherman gabriel august   the courtship the story behind the obamabrooks bromance the new republic retrieved september     brooks david october   run barack run the new york times retrieved september     in depth with david brooks cspan december   retrieved april   host so how is the president doing brooks you know i think im a little disappointed that he didnt do simpsonbowles i was a little disappointed in the way the debt has run up and i dont blame him for running up the debt in the recession but i think we needed an exit strategy to get out of it i think he could have done a little more to promote growth though i think given all the bad things it was going to be tough no matter who was president no matter who did anything it was going to be tough to promote growth so i dont particularly blame him for that i think hes conducted himself in pretty much an honest way hes had very little corruption i still have great personal admiration for him im more to his right but i give him no worse than a b i think hes made some mistakes but i wouldnt say hes been a bad president   i miss barack obama the new york times february     a b c brooks david january   the tel aviv cluster the new york times   maltz bovy phoebe david brooks was right antisemitism is a different evil the new republic retrieved august     a b brooks david may   the nature of poverty the new york times   a b schwartz ian june   david brooks people will be sick of trump and vote for hillary she will be competent and normal retrieved september     a b pbs news hour shields and brooks on ‘anticlimactic’ clinton victory trump’s ‘moral chasm’ online video clip youtube youtube  june  web  september   brooks david  march  no not trump not ever new york times retrieved  september    new york times april     brooks david november   the power of marriage the new york times retrieved may     brooks david april   postures in public facts in the womb the new york times retrieved december     brooks david january   weed been there done that the new york times   scocca tom david brooks has some notions about the programs on your television machine slate retrieved august     scocca tom david brooks is nostalgic for a world without himself in it slate retrieved august     issenberg sasha booboos in paradise philadelphia magazine retrieved november     zweig david the facts vs david brooks startling inaccuracies raise questions about his latest book salon retrieved august     kinsley michael suburban thrall new york times retrieved november     scocca tom david brooks has noticed hillary is a soviet dictator gawker archived from the original on august   retrieved august     lowery annie  may  david brooks is not buying your excuses poor people new york magazine retrieved  september    illing sean  may  why david brooks shouldn’t talk about poor people slate retrieved  september    a b taranto james brooks borks cruz wall street journal january    brooks david the brutalism of ted cruz new york times january    dretke v haley  us    althouse ann althouse january    denniston lyle constitution check did the supreme court give us super pacs constitution daily may    brooks david december   the sidney awards  the new york times retrieved december     the times’ ‘new york conservative’ the jewish week   brooks sarah june   whats in a name in part my religion washington jewish week   love etc david brooks and sarah brooks divorce washington post  november  retrieved  may    lamb brian  february  qa with david brooks cspan retrieved  may   lamb are you divorced or not brooks i am divorced yes and i dont want to personally i dont want to legally talk about it but yes i am divorced  i do believe in marriage mine didnt work out i desperately want to get married to somebody   new york times columnist david brooks weds his former researcher anne snyder washington post  april  retrieved  may    david brooks’ son is in the israeli army does it matter jewish journal september   retrieved september    external linksedit this sections use of external links may not follow wikipedias policies or guidelines please improve this article by removing excessive or inappropriate external links and converting useful links where appropriate into footnote references march  learn how and when to remove this template message wikimedia commons has media related to david brooks cultural commentator wikiquote has quotations related to david brooks cultural commentator david brooks at ted appearances on cspan in depth interview with brooks december   david brooks on charlie rose the transformation of david brooks columbia journalism review october   longform bio article on brooks david brooks on imdb works by or about david brooks in libraries worldcat catalog meet david brooks and column archive at the new york times discussion with andrew rosenthal frank rich and maureen dowd the new york times video july   column archive at the atlantic column archive at the weekly standard david brooks on the emily rooney show on wgbh radio video david brooks discusses the social animal the hidden sources of love character and achievement on march   on forum network ubben lecture at depauw university october   dead link heres a new source for this talk i am not charlie hebdo  the new york times the opinion pages oped columnist january   authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc  bnf cbp data nkc xx retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitledavidbrooksculturalcommentatoroldid categories  birthsliving peoplethcentury american journaliststhcentury american writersstcentury american jou