mment about sarah palin and her cancer on the republican party brooks yeah i do i think it was some lunch affair for some magazine and i was just mouthing off and so i  im not a fan of hers but thats a little strong   brooks david march   no uturns the new york times retrieved september     pareene alex blow up the times oped page and start again salon retrieved august     sherman gabriel august   the courtship the story behind the obamabrooks bromance the new republic retrieved september     brooks david october   run barack run the new york times retrieved september     in depth with david brooks cspan december   retrieved april   host so how is the president doing brooks you know i think im a little disappointed that he didnt do simpsonbowles i was a little disappointed in the way the debt has run up and i dont blame him for running up the debt in the recession but i think we needed an exit strategy to get out of it i think he could have done a little more to promote growth though i think given all the bad things it was going to be tough no matter who was president no matter who did anything it was going to be tough to promote growth so i dont particularly blame him for that i think hes conducted himself in pretty much an honest way hes had very little corruption i still have great personal admiration for him im more to his right but i give him no worse than a b i think hes made some mistakes but i wouldnt say hes been a bad president   i miss barack obama the new york times february     a b c brooks david january   the tel aviv cluster the new york times   maltz bovy phoebe david brooks was right antisemitism is a different evil the new republic retrieved august     a b brooks david may   the nature of poverty the new york times   a b schwartz ian june   david brooks people will be sick of trump and vote for hillary she will be competent and normal retrieved september     a b pbs news hour shields and brooks on ‘anticlimactic’ clinton victory trump’s ‘moral chas