y i dont want to legally talk about it but yes i am divorced  i do believe in marriage mine didnt work out i desperately want to get married to somebody   new york times columnist david brooks weds his former researcher anne snyder washington post  april  retrieved  may    david brooks’ son is in the israeli army does it matter jewish journal september   retrieved september    external linksedit this sections use of external links may not follow wikipedias policies or guidelines please improve this article by removing excessive or inappropriate external links and converting useful links where appropriate into footnote references march  learn how and when to remove this template message wikimedia commons has media related to david brooks cultural commentator wikiquote has quotations related to david brooks cultural commentator david brooks at ted appearances on cspan in depth interview with brooks december   david brooks on charlie rose the transformation of david brooks columbia journalism review october   longform bio article on brooks david brooks on imdb works by or about david brooks in libraries worldcat catalog meet david brooks and column archive at the new york times discussion with andrew rosenthal frank rich and maureen dowd the new york times video july   column archive at the atlantic column archive at the weekly standard david brooks on the emily rooney show on wgbh radio video david brooks discusses the social animal the hidden sources of love character and achievement on march   on forum network ubben lecture at depauw university october   dead link heres a new source for this talk i am not charlie hebdo  the new york times the opinion pages oped columnist january   authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc  bnf cbp data nkc xx retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitledavidbrooksculturalcommentatoroldid categories  birthsliving peoplethcentury american journaliststhcentury american writersstcentury american journali